These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, milk, 7up
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, basketball, sailing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
2. the person drinking soy-milk is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person drinking milk##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | 7up    | sprite    | milk |
| Sport      | badminton | skateboarding | sailing | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, 7up, fanta
There 4 different types of food: peas, spinach, raspberry, pomegranate
1. the person eating peas is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
3. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
4. the person drinking cola is not the person eating spinach##6
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | cola  | 7up    | lemonade | fanta    |
| Food       | pomegranate | spinach | raspberry  | peas |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, juice, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, mechanic, designer, teacher
1. the person drinking mirinda is not the security-guard##6
2. the mechanic is not the person drinking juice##6
3. the designer is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
4. the mechanic is the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the mechanic##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
7. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
8. the designer is somewhere to the left of the teacher##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda       | cola  | soy-milk  | juice |
| Job        | designer | teacher | mechanic | security-guard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, hamster, rabbit, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, van, motorbike, jet-ski
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
3. the person driving the jet-ski is not the owner of the hamster##6
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
6. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | hamster | rabbit | horse     | fish |
| Transport   | van     | motorbike    | taxi | jet-ski    |

