.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, coffee, juice
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi, helicopter, motorbike
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
3. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
4. the person drinking sprite is not the person driving the motorbike##6
5. the person driving the jet-ski is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate        | juice | coffee | sprite |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski | taxi     | helicopter   |

