.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, martial-arts, romance, family
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, canadian, russian, thai
1. the japanese is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is not the canadian##6
3. the japanese is on the far right##1
4. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the thai##5
5. the person watching romance movies is the person watching romance movies##1
6. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
7. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
9. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the thai##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | romance    | drama  | family   |
| Nationality   | russian  | thai | canadian | japanese |

