.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, scientific, horror, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, folk, indie
1. the fan folk is on the left or right of the fan metal##3
2. the fan folk is not the person watching scientific movies##6
3. the person watching drama movies is the fan r&b##1
4. the fan metal is on the left or right of the fan indie##3
5. the fan folk is on the far left##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is the fan metal##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the fan metal##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific     | horror | drama |
| Music-Genre   | folk | metal | indie      | r&b         |

