.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, nurse, accountant, pilot
1. the fisherman is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5
3. the pilot is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the nurse is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the nurse##3
6. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
7. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
8. the person drinking mirinda is not the pilot##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | cola        | lemonade      | water          |
| Job        | fisherman | nurse | pilot | accountant |

