.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, scientist, mechanic, electrician
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi, tram, train
1. the coach is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the taxi is not the electrician##6
3. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
4. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the train is the mechanic##1
7. the coach is not the person driving the train##6
8. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the electrician##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | coach  | mechanic | electrician    | scientist |
| Transport   | taxi | train | tram | jet-ski  |

