.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, bird, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, baseball, handball, tennis
1. the person who's sport is parkour is not the owner of the hamster##6
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the owner of the bird is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
6. the person who's sport is baseball is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
7. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the bird is the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | bird | hamster        | frog  | chinchilla     |
| Sport   | parkour     | tennis | baseball | handball |

