.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, hiking, sudoku, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, ambient, punk, r&b
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
2. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
3. the fan punk is not the person who's hobby is sudoku##6
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the fan r&b and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the fan ambient is between the fan techno and the person who's hobby is baking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | hiking    | baking | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | techno         | ambient | r&b   | punk     |

