.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, lime, apple, tomato
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, roller, taxi, ship
1. the person eating apple is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
2. the person eating tomato is not the person driving the boat##6
3. the person driving the roller is the person eating tomato##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person eating lime##1
5. the person driving the taxi is not the person eating tomato##6
6. the person eating lime is not the person driving the boat##6
7. the person eating apple is somewhere to the left of the person eating lime##5
8. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | mango  | apple | lime | tomato |
| Transport   | taxi | boat     | ship     | roller    |

