.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, orange, radish, blueberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, spy, sports
1. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
2. the person eating orange is not the person watching disaster movies##6
3. the person eating cranberry is the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person eating radish is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
5. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating orange and the person watching action movies##2
6. the person eating orange is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | blueberry | orange      | cranberry | radish   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | spy | sports   | action |

