.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, romance, sports, action
1. the person watching sports movies is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
2. the person watching sports movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person watching action movies is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking soy-milk##2
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk | mirinda     | almond-milk     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | sports       | action | romance |

