.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-15::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, bartender, project-manager, scientist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, soccer, snowboarding, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the teacher is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
3. the person who's sport is soccer is not the teacher##6
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the bartender and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the bartender is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
7. the scientist is on the right of the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | teacher  | project-manager | scientist | bartender |
| Sport   | tennis | soccer | snowboarding   | skateboarding |

