2. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the trike is not the person who's sport is badminton##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | tennis | cycling | badminton | baseball |
| Transport   | train   | motorbike       | skateboard    | trike     |

