The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, badminton, snowboarding, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person drinking sprite is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
8. the person drinking water is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | water    | tea | soy-milk | sprite         |
| Sport      | badminton | snowboarding | volleyball          | water-polo |

