.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, traveling, chess, photography
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog, ferret, dog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
2. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the dog is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
5. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | chess | reading | photography |
| Pet     | ferret  | hedgehog      | goldfish  | dog       |

