3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the trike is not the person drinking cola##6
5. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
6. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | cola | tea | fanta      | coffee   |
| Transport   | boat  | jet-ski   | airplane | trike |

 